>he uses <br>that one as much as he uses Narril. Second off, I suspect that it's <br>Narril as <br>Imagonner OR Poltara. Poltara is a terrible troll.<br><br>Next, some of them look down on MMDN, and I got the impression that <br>whole <br>thread that you put in the vault, was nothing more than elitest making <br>fun of <br>everyone here. Not that that is out of line, but, it surely could have <br>been <br>done less spammily.<br><br>Lastly, most of Wisdom's posts to MMDN are /exactly/ that - self <br>congradulatory <br>threads where they all brag about what they've done and how important <br>and cool <br>they are. And check out their bboards - now why would they keep posting <br>in <br>their non-private bboards (for all the world to see) each time they <br>think <br>they've gotten some bit or armor of killed some mob? Talk about <br>hypocritical.<br><br>Anyways, just my 2cents.<br><br><br>So basically... Were the last two threads the trolls of all time? <br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFF8DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub18.ezboard.com/ulehlumultipahs.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lehlu Multipahs</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.wisdomguild.org/images/narril/lehlu/lehlu_icon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>MithMarr Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#006400>(8/29/01 10:11:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=715.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.wisdomguild.org/images/narril/lehlu/lehlu_small.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_happydead.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: To Narril, Poltara and other wisdom guild members... </span><hr size=1> Hi, four quick points:<br><br>1) I am Narril's RL wife.<br>2) He occasionaly p